<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Women's Spa Services</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #ff99cc;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .service {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .service img {
            max-width: 120px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .service-info {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .service h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .service p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .service-price {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .service-details {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .read-more {
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .service button {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .service button:hover {
            background-color: #333;
        }

        .cart {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .cart h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        #cart-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        #cart-list li {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        #total {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Back navigation arrow */
        .back-arrow {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .remove-btn {
            background-color: #ff3333;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .remove-btn:hover {
            background-color: #cc0000;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Women's Spa Services</h1>
    </header>

    <section>
        <!-- Service 3 -->
        <div class="service" id="service3">
            <img src="Screenshot 2023-11-20 at 12.23.27 AM.png" alt="Pinda Sweda Detox Therapy">
            <div class="service-info">
                <h2>Pinda Sweda: Potli Detox Therapy</h2>
                <p>Enjoy the detoxifying benefits of Pinda Sweda, a therapy using herbal potlis.</p>
                <p class="service-price">Rs. 1200.00</p>
                <button onclick="addToCart('Pinda Sweda', 1200.00)" id="Pinda-sewa">Add to Cart</button>
                <span class="read-more" onclick="toggleDetails('service3-details')">Read More</span>
                <div class="service-details" id="service3-details">
                    <p>Pinda Sweda involves the use of herbal potlis (bundles) filled with medicated herbs. The therapy helps in detoxification, pain relief, and enhancing blood circulation.</p>
                    <p>Additional Benefits:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Relief from joint pain</li>
                        <li>Skin rejuvenation</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 4 -->
        <div class="service" id="service4">
            <img src="Screenshot 2023-11-20 at 12.23.42 AM.png" alt="Meditative Abhyanga Calming Therapy">
            <div class="service-info">
                <h2>Meditative Abhyanga: Calming Therapy</h2>
                <p>Experience a calming and meditative massage to relax the body and mind.</p>
                <p class="service-price">Rs. 850.00</p>
                <button onclick="addToCart('Meditative Abhyanga', 850.00)" id="abhyanga">Add to Cart</button>
                <span class="read-more" onclick="toggleDetails('service4-details')">Read More</span>
                <div class="service-details" id="service4-details">
                    <p>Meditative Abhyanga combines gentle massage techniques with calming Ayurvedic oils to promote relaxation and reduce stress. The therapy aims to bring balance to the mind and body.</p>
                    <p>Additional Benefits:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Mental relaxation</li>
                        <li>Improved sleep quality</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 5 -->
        <div class="service" id="service5">
            <img src="Screenshot 2023-11-20 at 12.24.00 AM.png" alt="Sand Khizhi Soothing Therapy">
            <div class="service-info">
                <h2>Sand Khizhi: Soothing Sand Potli Therapy</h2>
                <p>Enjoy a soothing therapy using sand potlis for relaxation and rejuvenation.</p>
                <p class="service-price">Rs. 1100.00</p>
                <button onclick="addToCart('Sand Khizhi', 1100.00)" id="therapy">Add to Cart</button>
                <span class="read-more" onclick="toggleDetails('service5-details')">Read More</span>
                <div class="service-details" id="service5-details">
                    <p>Sand Khizhi involves the use of potlis filled with warm sand. The therapy is known for its soothing and rejuvenating effects, promoting muscle relaxation and relieving stiffness.</p>
                    <p>Additional Benefits:</p>
